n pipeline (`lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`, 1577 lines) has these stages:\n\n1. **Preprocessing**: Skip garbled burst (short OCR noise at start)\n2. **Pre-merge**: Join continuation lines (e.g., `PIZZA / VARIATION`)\n3. **Candidate generation**: Single lines + 2-line and 3-line joins\n4. **Hard filters**: 9 independent checks (length, ingredients, metadata, OCR quality, sections, etc.)\n5. **Pre-filter cap**: Limit to 25 candidates, preferring ALL_CAPS and short ones\n6. **Embedding scoring**: Semantic similarity to \"recipe name, dish title...\" minus header/noise similarity\n7. **Bonuses**: Position (multiplicative x1.0-1.12), ALL_CAPS (+0.08), structural (+0.10)\n8. **Bilingual detection**: Suppress ALL_CAPS translations that conflict with mixed-case titles\n9. **Threshold filtering**: max(0.08, bestThresholdScore × 0.7)\n10. **Post-threshold cleanup**: Remove prefixes, join protection, sub-section removal\n11. **Dedup**: Shorter substring wins\n12. **Multi-title guard**: Check ingredient gaps, corroboration\n13. **Final sort & join**: Return up to 3 titles joined with \" + \"\n\n### Recent Implementation Improvements\n\n**Iteration 27→28 changes (planned but status unclear):**\n- Iteration 27 added \"direct-successor bonus\" for lines immediately following section headers\n- Working toward fixing OCR blind repair for early-position candidates\n- Planned: Extend corroboration to check post-spillover text only\n\n**Language support:**\n- English: 80+ measurement units, metadata patterns (SERVES, PREP TIME, etc.)\n- Polish: 40+ units (łyżka, szklanka, szczypta), metadata (NA, DLA, MIN, GODZ), section labels (SKŁADNIKI, PRZYGOTOWANIE)\n\n### Failure Analysis Detail\n\n**Iteration 26 feedback** (16 generated failures, 0 real):\n- Spillover corruption: 5 failures (empty extraction when page starts with previous recipe)\n- Heavy digit corruption: 2 failures (titles with dense digit substitution rejected)\n- Wrong body text: 3 failures (partial corruption causes fallback to instructions/serving text)\n- Section headers: 3 failures (category headers like FISH & SEAFOOD scored too high)\n- Multi-line title truncation: 1 failure (only first line extracted)\n- Mid-recipe pages: 2 failures (multiple recipes on same page)\n\n**Iteration 27 feedback** (11 generated, 0 real):\n- Same core patterns as iteration 26, suggesting the improvements didn't fully resolve root causes\n\n### File Locations\n\n- Implementation: `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts`\n- Iteration tracking: `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/iter.txt`\n- Recent feedback:\n  - Iteration 28: `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/28-1ac016c/feedback.md` (5.3KB)\n  - Iteration 27: `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/27-51f970e/feedback.md` (4.3KB)\n  - Iteration 27 plan: `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/27-51f970e/improvement-plan.md` (18KB, very detailed)\n- Architecture docs: `/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/docs/architecture.md`\n\n### Key Insights\n\n1. **Real vs synthetic gap**: 100% success on real files but plateau on generated tests suggests the synthetic test generation may not fully replicate real OCR patterns\n2. **Diminishing returns on dictionary approach**: Iteration 24-26 expanded food dictionary but OCR failures persist - blind repair may be needed\n3. **Position bonus limitations**: Current multiplicative position bonus (x1.0-1.12) insufficient to overcome semantic similarity scores of descriptive text\n4. **Spillover detection gap**: Can detect explicit markers but implicit spillover (pages starting mid-instruction) not fully caught\n5. **Compound architecture stability**: The pipeline has ~1500 lines of carefully balanced heuristics; each fix risks subtle regressions elsewhere\n\nThe improvement plan for iteration 28 is thorough and well-documented, with 4 targeted fixes, implementation order, and testing strategy already mapped out."}],"totalDurationMs":74848,"totalTokens":114885,"totalToolUseCount":19,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2965,"cache_read_input_tokens":110143,"output_tokens":1772,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2965},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
