{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01N7BRHGHkNv4BX7RAmLUBPc","type":"tool_result","content":"VEGETABLES\n\nRoasted Asparagus with Parmesan\n\nSimple yet elegant vegetable dish that complements\nany main course. Perfect for spring and early summer.\n\nIngredients:\n- 2 lbs (900g) fresh asparagus,\n  trimmed\n- 3 tablespoons olive oil\n- 4 cloves garlic, minced\n- 1/2 cup grated parmesan cheese\n- 1/2 teaspoon red pepper flakes\n- Zest of 1 lemon\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n- Fresh basil leaves\n\nInstructions:\nPreheat oven to 425°F (220°C).\nToss asparagus with olive oil, garlic, salt, pepper.\nSpread on baking sheet in single layer.\nRoast 12-15 minutes until tender-crisp. 45\nSprinkle with parmesan, lemon zest, pepper flakes.\nReturn to oven for 2 minutes.\nGarnish with fresh basil.\nServes 4-6.\nBest served immediately while warm.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b1b8cabe-82af-4d43-a6df-d4a8ec65d151","uuid":"1414c609-cb9e-49ad-ad1d-b0b9611b92d8","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"VEGETABLES\n\nRoasted Asparagus with Parmesan\n\nSimple yet elegant vegetable dish that complements\nany main course. Perfect for spring and early summer.\n\nIngredients:\n- 2 lbs (900g) fresh asparagus,\n  trimmed\n- 3 tablespoons olive oil\n- 4 cloves garlic, minced\n- 1/2 cup grated parmesan cheese\n- 1/2 teaspoon red pepper flakes\n- Zest of 1 lemon\n- Salt and pepper to taste\n- Fresh basil leaves\n\nInstructions:\nPreheat oven to 425°F (220°C).\nToss asparagus with olive oil, garlic, salt, pepper.\nSpread on baking sheet in single layer.\nRoast 12-15 minutes until tender-crisp. 45\nSprinkle with parmesan, lemon zest, pepper flakes.\nReturn to oven for 2 minutes.\nGarnish with fresh basil.\nServes 4-6.\nBest served immediately while warm.","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}}
